text = "Uh oh!\nSeems like whoever worked as the hospital manager got angry and broke all of our equipment...\nNow its up to you to handle dispatch and place patients in the emergency room on this old rusty machine!\nUse the dispatch screen to send ambulances to pick up patients\n(Note: you only need to write the patients name and adress)\nEach ambulance fits 2 patients at a time, but keep in mind that if you send it to 2 far away locations the patient might not survive...\n\nAfter a patient gets hospitalized your job is not done!\nUsing the emergency room screen you must discharge the patient for it to count!\nBut you cant just discharge them anytime... you must wait for them to be stable, unless you wanna stay pointless!\n\nImportant: You gotta get off the pc to connect the phone to the pc (click pc screen)\nYou can make 3 mistakes before you get fired... how many lives can you save before that????\n\nPro tip: if its too easy try the one tab only challenge";


